e self force to examine resonant and near resonant strong-field\neffects in greater depth, which will be needed to characterize how a binary\nevolves through orbital resonances.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Aug 2012 00:05:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 26 Feb 2014 19:59:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-12-09"}
